{{see|Armpit}}
==English==

===Etymology===
From '''[[arm]]''' plus '''[[pit]]'''

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The cavity beneath the junction of the arm and shoulder.
# Somewhere or something considered foul.
#: '' The '''armpit''' of America.''

====Synonyms====
*[[under-arm]], [[underarm]]
*[[axilla]]
*[[oxter]]

